<plot>Ginette Schenk lives in the margins of the East Village. Her dog Schatzy seems to be the only thing she has and loves. "Water in the Boat" presents a collection of moments from their daily walk to the park. Days move slowly, autumn turns winter, as Ginette struggles to smile and keep herself together.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?648449</url></doc>
